'''安东尼·麦凯'''（{{lang-en|'''Anthony Mackie'''}}<ref name=ref064>{{cite web |url=http://files.usgwarchives.net/la/orleans/obits/2006/2006-04.txt |title=April 2006 Obituaries Orleans Parish Louisiana |accessdate=2013-03-30 |work=usgwarchives.net |archive-date=2012-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120719073038/http://files.usgwarchives.net/la/orleans/obits/2006/2006-04.txt |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，{{bd|1978年|9月23日||}}<ref name=inyt>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2003/02/23/theater/spring-theater-performance-class-clown-makes-good-quietly.html |title=SPRING THEATER: PERFORMANCE; Class Clown Makes Good, Quietly |first=Jonathan |last=Mandell |date=2003-02-23 |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |accessdate=2013-03-30 |archive-date=2013-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131220232754/http://www.nytimes.com/2003/02/23/theater/spring-theater-performance-class-clown-makes-good-quietly.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>http://articles.nydailynews.com/2006-08-06/entertainment/18344525_1_drug-dealers-anthony-mackie-half-nelson{{dead link|date=March 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=KNk8AAAAIBAJ&sjid=IS4MAAAAIBAJ&pg=4610,2302814&dq=anthony-mackie+28&hl=en |title=Up & Comers: Meet Anthony Mackie |newspaper=[[Bangor_Daily_News|Bangor Daily News]] |date=2006-12-22 |last=Gajewski |first=Josh |page=12 |accessdate=2013-03-30}}</ref>），是一位美国演员，曾出演过多部电影、电视剧、[[百老汇|百老汇]]和[[外百老汇|外百老汇]]戏剧，2002年获得[[奥比奖|奥比奖]]（Obie Award）。

2002年，他出演了[[埃米纳姆|埃米纳姆]]参演的处女作《[[8英里|8英里]]》。2009年因出演《[[拆弹部队|拆弹部队]]》，他被提名2009年[[独立精神奖|独立精神奖]]最佳男配角。

== 早年 ==
麦基出生在[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]][[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]市<ref name=allmovie>{{Cite web|title=Anthony Mackie – Overview|work=[[Allmovie|Allmovie]]|url=http://www.allmovie.com/artist/anthony-mackie-347951|accessdate=2009-06-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090611043531/http://www.allmovie.com/artist/anthony-mackie-347951|archivedate=2009-06-11|deadurl=no}}</ref>，是戈登·玛莎（Gordon Martha）和经营着一间装修公司的老威利·麦基（Willie Mackie，Sr.）的儿子<ref name=ref064/><ref name=edi>{{Cite web | title = Anthony Mackie: Biography | publisher = TV Guide | url = http://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/anthony-mackie/bio/140378 | access-date = 2010-09-02 | archive-date = 2009-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090127020016/http://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/anthony-mackie/bio/140378 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.diylife.com/2011/07/20/anthony-mackie-nobar/ |title=Interview With Anthony Mackie, Bar Owner, Actor, DIY Enthusiast |last=Preiser |first=Amy |accessdate=2013-03-20 |work=Homesessive |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120718153844/http://www.diylife.com/2011/07/20/anthony-mackie-nobar/ |archive-date=2012-07-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。麦基就读于新奥尔良创作艺术中心（NOCCA），1997年从北卡罗来纳州艺术学校高中戏剧班毕业<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.uncsa.edu/drama/alumni.htm#AnthonyMackie |title=School of Drama Alumni |work=uncsa.edu |accessdate=2013-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130127043412/http://uncsa.edu/drama/alumni.htm#AnthonyMackie |archive-date=2013-01-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。后来，他从[[朱利亚德学院|朱利亚德学院]]戏剧科第30组毕业（1997年-2001年），[[李·培斯|李·培斯]]和[[特蕾西·托马斯|特蕾西·托马斯]]是他的同班同学<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.juilliard.edu/journal/qa-anthony-mackie |title=Q&A With Anthony Mackie |journal=[[The_Juilliard_School|The Juilliard School]] |last=Pedlow |first=Amelia |date=April 2010 |accessdate=2013-03-30 |archive-date=2014-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141030050404/http://www.juilliard.edu/journal/qa-anthony-mackie |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.juilliard.edu/journal/14553 |title=Alumni News for May 2008 |date=May 2008 |work=The Juilliard Journal |accessdate=2013-03-30 |journal= |archive-date=2014-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141211020031/http://www.juilliard.edu/journal/14553 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 職業生涯 ==
麦凯在[[漫威影业|漫威影业]]电影《[[美国队长2|美国队长2]]》、《[[复仇者联盟2：奥创纪元|复仇者联盟2：奥创纪元]]》、《[[蟻人_(電影)|蟻人]]》、《[[美國隊長3：英雄內戰|美國隊長3：英雄內戰]]》、《[[復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰|復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰]]》和《[[復仇者聯盟：終局之戰|復仇者聯盟：終局之戰]]》中饰演[[猎鹰_(漫画)|猎鹰]]一角<ref name="CaptainATWS">{{cite web |url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118056643 |title=Mackie mulls Falcon in 'Captain America' |first=Marc |last=Graser |publisher=Variety |date=2012-07-16 |accessdate=2012-07-17 |archive-date=2012-07-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69DyO1q9R?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118056643 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/shadowandact/anthony-mackie-confirmed-to-play-falcon-in-captain-america-sequel |title=Anthony Mackie Confirmed To Play Falcon In 'Captain America' Sequel |work=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]] |first=Tambay A. |last=Obenson |date=2012-09-13 |accessdate=2015-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304110232/http://blogs.indiewire.com/shadowandact/anthony-mackie-confirmed-to-play-falcon-in-captain-america-sequel |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

== 私生活 ==
麦凯与其交往多年的女友在2009年春季生下一孩。2011年夏季，他在纽约市[[布鲁克林|布鲁克林]]开办了一个名为“NoBar”的酒吧。
<ref>{{cite news|last=Mathias|first=Christopher|title=Anthony Mackie Opens Up 'NoBar' In Bed-Stuy, Brooklyn|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/07/20/anthony-mackie-opens-up-n_n_904646.html|newspaper=[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]]|date=2011-07-20|accessdate=2015-04-26|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924144725/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/07/20/anthony-mackie-opens-up-n_n_904646.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

他的哥哥{{le|加尔文·麦凯|Calvin Mackie}}是[[杜兰大学|杜兰大学]]一名副教授。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.channelzro.com/about.htm |title=Calvin Mackie - About Calvin |work=channelzro.com |accessdate=2015-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150204033401/http://channelzro.com/about.htm |archive-date=2015-02-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2013年11月9日凌晨，麦凯因涉嫌酒驾在[[哈林区|哈林区]]被捕<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/anthony-mackie-arrested-charged-driving-654866 |title=Anthony Mackie Arrested, Charged With Driving While Intoxicated |work=hollywoodreporter.com/ |accessdate=2013-11-11 |archive-date=2013-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110001605/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/anthony-mackie-arrested-charged-driving-654866 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

